@imsurprisedtoo I have anxiety too. Some things you can do until you get into see someone. 
Take a yoga or exercise class together
Take a walk in nature. 
Limit Screen time, especially social media.
Do arts and crafts or bake together. 
Sing and dance real silly

Good luck.
